  "name": "Attuned to the Ancestors (Scarab Sages)",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/environment/people/charge.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\">You were raised to believe that undead are nothing to fear&mdash;they are simply the unliving remnants of your honored ancestors.</span></p></em>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>Scarab Sages</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\">Benefits</span></strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\"><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\">Once per day, you can surround yourself with an aura of unlife. Unintelligent undead ignore you unless you take action against them, per hide from undead. The protection lasts 1 round for every two character levels you possess (with a minimum of 1 round). If you take any offensive action against any undead, this effect immediately ends. This is a supernatural ability.</span><br /></span></p>",
